            </p>
          </WideCard>
          <WideCard title="Studium generale et sociale"
                    description="Oct 2018 – July 2019"
                    org="Leibniz Kolleg Tübingen"
                    imageSrc=""
                    href="https://uni-tuebingen.de/einrichtungen/verwaltung/stabsstellen/leibniz-kolleg/das-leibniz-kolleg/"
                    pos=""
                    topics={[]}>
          </WideCard>
          <WideCard title="Carlo-Schmid-Gymnasium Tübingen"
                    description="2010 – 2018"
                    org=""
                    imageSrc=""
                    href="https://csg-tuebingen.de"
                    pos=""
                    topics={[]}>
            <p>Final grade: 1.0</p>
            <p>Received a price for the best Abitur in Chemistry.</p>
          </WideCard>
        </ol>
      </Section>
      <footer id="colophon" class="-f-m-xl f-p-xl rounded-xl f-text-xs text-zinc-400 transition-all target:bg-zinc-700 ease-in-out duration-700">
        <p class="f-mb-xs">
          Written in <Ol href="https://github.com/doomemacs/doomemacs">Doom Emacs</Ol> on a <Ol href="https://github.com/andrewjrae/rae-dux">rae-dux keyboard</Ol> with a <Ol href="https://github.com/haglobah/zmk-config-tzcl">custom layout</Ol> while standing upright thanks to <Ol href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iOupyi-lQZM">Ben Vallack</Ol>. Built with <Ol href="https://astro.build/">Astro</Ol> and <Ol href="https://unocss.dev/">UnoCSS</Ol> with <Ol href="https://utopia.fyi/blog/designing-with-fluid-type-scales/">Fluid Type Scales</Ol> on <Ol href="https://nixos.org/">NixOS</Ol>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Layout and Design heavily inspired by <Ol href="https://brittanychiang.com">Brittany Chiang</Ol>.
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
